OL,5,G1300 A Place in the Sun
OL,6,     FJonnie Irwin house-hunts around
OL,7,     Fthe hilltop town of Competa, in
OL,8,     Fsouthern Spain, with Michael and
OL,9,     FSeamus from Northern Ireland. They
OL,10,     Fwant a holiday home with space to
OL,11,     Fentertain for #175k.
OL,12,G1400 A Place in the Sun
