OL,5,G1820 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FThe competition begins in
OL,7,     FNorthumberland, where
OL,8,     Fkaraoke-loving hosts Darren and
OL,9,     FBobby hope to hit the high notes
OL,10,     Fwith their home-from-home B&B and
OL,11,     Fa visit to Hexham Abbey.
OL,12,G1855 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FDaniella and Angela host at their
OL,14,     Fhotel in East Lothian, where
OL,15,     Fthere's a chill in the air when
OL,16,     Fthe B&Bers take on a rope obstacle
OL,17,     Fcourse suspended over open water.
OL,18,G1925 Four in a Bed
OL,19,     FIn Blackpool, Paul and entertainer
OL,20,     FVictoria are keen to extol the
OL,21,     Fvirtues of the seaside town, via
OL,22,     Fthe mediums of bingo and karaoke.
